    {
        "content": "<p>TartanLlama opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12735\">PR #12735</a> from <code>TartanLlama:sy/concurrent-host-calls</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Currently, the waitable set that is used for waiting on sync-lowered, async-implemented host functions is a property of <code>GuestTask</code>. As such, if multiple threads within the same task make concurrent synchronous calls to host functions that block, this state can become corrupted. This PR moves this waitable set into <code>GuestThread</code> to enable this pattern.</p>\n</blockquote>",
